Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:09.27,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:12.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.92,0:00:16.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:24.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.27,0:00:34.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:41.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.99,0:00:48.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.95,0:00:56.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.09,0:00:59.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:03.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.43,0:01:07.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.43,0:01:10.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:14.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:18.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.19,0:01:21.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.19,0:01:25.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.70,0:01:29.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.41,0:01:32.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:35.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.67,0:01:41.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:49.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.98,0:01:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, were you able\Nto find any medicinal herbs?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.44,0:01:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. I've collected most of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there may be even rarer ones on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.11,0:02:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, something's\Nbeen bugging me for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.24,0:02:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what this weird groove\Nis that runs down this path...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, yeah, I wonder what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks as if a bicycle passed by.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.79,0:02:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're suddenly out in a large open space.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.35,0:02:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A raccoon dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a reindeer! See? I've got antlers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Chopper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.02,0:02:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, what happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.11,0:02:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.07,0:02:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who's that huge guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:03:02.20,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Navy Headquarters Admiral Aokiji!\NThe Ferocity of an Ultimate Powerhouse"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that he got Robin this shaken up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.94,0:03:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.08,0:03:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a marine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.16,0:03:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navy Headquarters Admiral... Aokiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Admiral?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.79,0:03:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A... Admiral? He's that high up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.38,0:03:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're only three officers in the Navy\Nwho hold the position of Admiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:03:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akainu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aokiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:04:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kizaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one above them
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is Fleet Admiral Sengoku, who reigns\Nas the top official in the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man is one of the three men
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,called the World Government's\Nultimate powerhouses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.99,0:04:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why is someone like that here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go deal with big-time pirates\Nwith several-hundred-million-Berry bounties?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G... Go someplace else!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.71,0:04:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's another sexy lady with super\Nbig bazongas! Are you free tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.01,0:04:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea, you tall, lanky jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay attention, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec, you guys, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear what I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I just took a stroll, didn't I?\NDon't get so worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.03,0:04:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To start with, you guys are...\Nwhatchamacallit... you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Wh-Whatchamacallit"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You know..."?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot. Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't make much sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck's with this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.87,0:05:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Robin, aren't you\Nmistaking him for someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way someone\Nlike him is a Navy Admiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey... Don't judge\Nothers by their appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My motto as a marine is "total slovenly justice."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.51,0:05:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That totally matches your appearance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me for a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Standing made me tired. Umph.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why were you sleeping standing up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, to make a long story short,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of capturing\Nyou guys, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to check the whereabouts
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of Nico Robin, who disappeared\Nafter the Alabasta incident, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought, she's been with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.75,0:05:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy sure is apathetic, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His audacity shows he's a leader,\Nin a manner of speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to at least report\Nthis to Headquarters, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as with another wanted person, the total\Nbounty for you guys has now changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:06:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,100 million... plus 60 million...\Nplus 79 million equals...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know exactly, but I'm\Nsure it's not too shabby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.90,0:06:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you calculate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec! Hold on, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.57,0:06:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! What're you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point in us picking a fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's one of the strongest marines!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?! Then are you saying we're\Ngonna hand over Robin without a fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you guys... I'm saying I'm\Nnot gonna do anything, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna beat him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So you're a marine...\NI wish you had told us sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hm?\N--Who are these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get hold of yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then this isn't an uninhabited island?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:07:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they're probably the passengers\Nwho drifted here from a wrecked ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About a month ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was a report that a passenger\Nliner went missing in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are they, Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're some injured people,\Nbut their wounds aren't serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be fine once I apply the medicine I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, it seems that\Nthey haven't been eating well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.26,0:07:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're weakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun and Usopp went to get some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must've been really hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to wolf down the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's plenty more where that came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! There's plenty more!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you eating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, even if this is an uninhabited island,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you are so inclined,\Nyou can find food, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the problem with amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised that you survived\Nafter a shipwreck in the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:08:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the only ones who made it to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On our way back from a gourmet\Ntour to the gourmet town, Pucci...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...our ship collided with a huge frog\Nthat was doing the front crawl
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.15,0:08:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and shattered into pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing the front crawl?! A frog was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frogs normally do the breaststroke, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.78,0:08:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting! I wanna see it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are you out of your mind?\N--It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Yokozuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--Yokozuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, after a great struggle,\Nwe were able to make it to this island,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yet we lived on the verge\Nof starvation for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.63,0:08:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We rejoiced when we saw someone was coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when we looked carefully,\Nhe was riding a bicycle on the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.22,0:08:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now... Under no\Ncircumstances can one ride a...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... that was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--And then, the next one\Nthat came was a pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:08:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Us, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:09:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you guys are... whatchamacallit...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you know... um... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.62,0:09:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it clearly! Clearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shoot! I totally forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Don't mess with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--L-Luffy! Hold on! Hold on!\N--Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.21,0:09:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said several times already, I took a stroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.63,0:09:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it was a stroll? Then don't go\Npassing a place like this! Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy kinda has the upper hand here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then... Okay.\NI'm going back, but before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, get ready to depart right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, there's an inhabited\Nisland not so far from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should go there to get\Nthe treatment you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys! You don't have to\Nlisten to this guy! He's a marine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:10:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... That's right. It's fine,\Nit's fine. That's right. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, marines are your friends\Nand we are the bad guys, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.64,0:10:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no time for laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'd help those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But does he have a ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides ours, I didn't see\Nany other ships anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no ship. They don't\Nhave a Log Pose, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are they supposed to\Ngo to that nearby island?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing you say sounds convincing, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.29,0:10:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that man can make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, done!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We loaded up food and water.\NWith this much, you'll be fine for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to work once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.44,0:11:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it feels good! You're quite a sensible guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hit it off with him after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what're you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.07,0:11:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna swim while\Npulling these guys and this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Step back a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.64,0:11:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sea animal! I bet that's the\Nguardian of this area of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Hey, you! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out! Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.16,0:12:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Age...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Fruit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.23,0:12:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The sea... froze!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the power of a\NNavy Headquarters' Admiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will probably last at least a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your time and head in that direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get to an inhabited island in four days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.66,0:13:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little cold, so dress warmly while walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea has become ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.59,0:13:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can now cross the sea!\NWe can get off of this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Marine! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a miracle! A miracle without doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.78,0:14:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, we'll get going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm happy for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.66,0:14:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.29,0:14:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there're different kinds of pirates, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.71,0:14:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't thank you enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.88,0:14:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did you treat our injured,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you also shared your\Nfood and water with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that even a chance meeting is\Ndue to karma from a previous life, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.72,0:14:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take good care of the children\Nso that they don't catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this state, the food will\Nprobably stay fresh for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.11,0:14:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bye-bye!\N--Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Thank you!\N--We'll never forget your kindness,\NStraw Hat Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya! Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful on your trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.12,0:14:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, it's cold. It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is completely like winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can ice skate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! That's amazing, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you'd expect from\Nsomeone born on a winter island!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:14:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.01,0:15:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, it's cold, it's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.43,0:15:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.23,0:15:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it... You're just\Nlike your gramps, Monkey D. Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.49,0:15:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're free-spirited, or should\NI say you're hard to figure out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gramps...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps...?! Luffy's?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the matter, Luffy?\NYou're drenched in sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.51,0:15:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... N-N-Nothing. Um... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.59,0:15:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your gramps really helped me out a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I came here was to\Nhave a look at Nico Robin and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On second thought...\Nmaybe you should die now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:16:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The government is still taking you guys lightly,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if I delve into your history, I can\Ntell that your group has a backbone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although your group is small,\Nsince it's gathering shrewd members,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll probably become a problem later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The circumstances that initially\Nled to your search orders...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the actions you took up until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The speed of your group's progress...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been dealing with outlaws for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it worries me to think how you'll turn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's too sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said earlier that you just\Ncame to check things out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I especially regard\Nyou guys as dangerous is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you, Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.03,0:16:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're after Robin after all!\NI'm gonna beat the crap out of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her bounty amount isn't just\Nan indication of her strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It also indicates the level of danger\Nshe poses to the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:17:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you got a 79-million-Berry\Nbounty on your head at the age of eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed that you survived as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You betrayed people and ran away.\NYou gained people's favor and used them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've survived in the underworld\Nby being quick to switch sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the group that you\Nchose as your next hideout, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you jerk! How insulting you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.82,0:17:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What grudge do you hold against Robin-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any grudge against her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we are somehow connected...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's that I let her get\Naway once, that's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys will eventually realize it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the not-so-distant future, you'll regret\Nthat you took in a troublesome woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.26,0:17:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As proof, the organizations Nico Robin\Nhad something to do with up until today
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all got annihilated... except for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:18:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why... Nico Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you jerk! Her past doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right! If you're worried about others' pasts,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.78,0:18:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can't be friends with ruffians like\Na pirate hunter or a former thief girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ruffians" was unnecessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more important is\Nthe present, rather than the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin is our precious friend now!\NDon't badmouth our friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.09,0:18:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... You really did a\Ngood job befriending this lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.88,0:18:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get to the point already! If you\Nwant to capture me, go ahead and do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.26,0:18:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treinta Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.93,0:18:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, my... Maybe I talked too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How disappointing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had too high an opinion of you,\Nthinking you were a little smarter than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.48,0:18:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clutch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! He shattered into pieces and died!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... We're screwed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:19:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Guys! Run! Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Saber!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.53,0:19:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't going to kill you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slice Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.05,0:19:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! How dare you butt in, you damn cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.39,0:19:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same to you, you natural monument!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:20:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,0:20:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He froze them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those three... all at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.35,0:20:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, no! They have to be treated right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they get frostbite, their limbs\Nwill become gangrenous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Usopp?!\NWe have to go help those three now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.36,0:20:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I really would like to,\Nbut my body can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I get frozen, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You're just too scared to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.74,0:20:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy!\N--Sanji! Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.78,0:20:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've come across some good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.58,0:21:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're still you, Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...! I'm no longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.42,0:21:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin! Watch out! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.39,0:21:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.64,0:21:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.98,0:22:09.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A piece of a dream that we started grasping
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:12.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:18.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We send our aspirations sailing into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:20.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we're exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:23.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a compass that can\Nsearch for something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:29.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think we can keep it forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.13,0:22:32.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the dream\Nthat we will reach someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:35.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to be adults as we\Nare now as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.09,0:22:37.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We pray to this endless sky that we look up at
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.80,0:22:40.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.89,0:22:43.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild fantasies from our childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:46.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We trace unforgettable memories
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.52,0:22:52.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And try to keep the embers\Nburning that still consume us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.19,0:22:55.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To this familiar sunny sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.11,0:22:57.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Together we entrust our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:23:00.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We go beyond the changing time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.41,0:23:08.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Robin got...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.96,0:23:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.17,0:23:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't yell! Her death will benefit the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.05,0:23:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What'd you say?!\N--You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.09,0:23:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wait, you guys!\N--Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere in this fight!\NI'll fight him in a duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.93,0:23:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine by me, but...\Nerr... whatchamacallit...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.64,0:23:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.85,0:23:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Duel between Rubber and Ice! Luffy vs. Aokiji"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.44,0:23:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
